INTRODUCTION
This project is a simple chatbot application that uses the OpenAI API to generate responses based on user input.
It consists of:

A Python backend (example.py) built with FastAPI

A frontend with two pages (Home and Chat) built using HTML/CSS/JS

A basic interface that sends messages to the backend and displays AI responses

A lightweight architecture suitable for learning, experimenting, and extending

SETUP
python3 --version
python3 -m ensurepip --upgrade
python3 -m pip install --upgrade pip
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
